data.description: Assumable VA Loan @2.75%.  (Property also qualifies for USDA). 1% rate buy down for the 1st year (see attachment for more details)    Welcome to 300 Northview. Built by Ashton Woods, 2023 Builder of the Year by Builder Magazine, this splendid 5-bedroom, 3-bathroom home in Georgetown, perfectly blending modern luxury with natural beauty.  Situated in the sought-after MorningStar neighborhood, enjoy a tranquil suburban lifestyle with easy access to downtown Georgetown's charm.    Five bedrooms and three bathrooms offer ample space, with a thoughtfully designed layout for privacy and togetherness.  The open concept kitchen and living room create an open, bright space.  Upstairs, you'll find three of the bedrooms, as well as a loft area that can be used as a second living room or play area.    Backing onto a greenbelt, enjoy serene natural views and tranquility in the expansive backyard with a covered patio that is ideal for outdoor enjoyment and entertaining.    A standout feature of this property is its immediate access to a community pool, providing the luxury of a refreshing swim just steps from your doorstep and a ton of other recreational activities, including a soccer field, playgrounds and trails. It's the perfect spot for gathering with friends on sun-filled Texas days.    Experience suburban serenity and modern convenience at 300 Northview. Schedule a showing today to make it your forever home!
